<p>Chloe's clip appears to have been filmed on Thursday while she was enjoying a day by the pool with her MTV co-star Bethan Kershaw. </p>

<p>The two beauties have been sharing regular updates from their Marbella getaway on Instagram, treating their fans to regular swimwear snaps.</p>

