<p>The reality star's girly getaway comes after she ignored speculation she had faked a trip to Ibiza and had instead secretly joined her ex Sam Gowland, 25, in Dubai.</p>

<p>Beach babes: Earlier in the day, the girls flaunted their figures in skimpy swimwear as they soaked up the sun at their resort</p>

